title: Grateful Dead Live at Delta Center on 1995-02-21

reviews.review_text:
excellent show One of my favorite shows for many a year. Probably my favorite version of Friend of the Devil.Excellent solos by everybody including Vince and an excellent solo by Jerry. Crisp soundboard is great but I was hunting for an audience and this is a really good source. If you don't know this show get to know it

Set 2 highlights 

Top version of Foolish and Trucking is hellacious.... avg space for 95... visions is great (is this the best one?)
